			"special_bonus_attack_speed_40"		"The Attack Speed is for the late-game as Storm Spirit starts to rely on his auto-attack to follow-through on his attacks."
			"storm_spirit_static_remnant"		"Use Static Remnant:

1. After Electric Vortex to force enemies to get hit by your remnant.
2. To activate an Overload attack, more damage and slow
3. In the trees to scout hidden enemies trying to juke
4. During the laning phase to farm groups of creeps with Overload.

Can trigger on invisible units. 
Use this ability to farm."
			"storm_spirit_electric_vortex"		"When casting Electric Vortex, you are also free to move or cast other abilities such as Static Remnant (which is a common combination that works at levels 3-4 of Vortex).

This is your disable and also activates an Overload charge."
			"storm_spirit_overload"		"Attack after this is triggered. The combination to gank works as such:

1. Ball Lightning towards an enemy, then auto-attack Overload
2. Electric Vortex and Static Remnant, then auto-attack Overload
3. Reposition with Ball Lightning then auto-attack Overload

Dont forget your Orchid of Malevolence if you bought it"
			"storm_spirit_ball_lightning"		"Use Ball Lightning to move around the map. To initiate or to get away. Be sure to leave enough mana for you to do your other abilities. This can go over cliffs or through trees.

This ability can also be used while simultaneously using your items such as Shivas Guard or Orchid of Malevolence."
